No!

20:46.417 --> 20:49.083
But, Baloo, what about your birds?

20:49.166 --> 20:51.417
Hey, what's more important,

20:51.500 --> 20:55.250
those burping buzzards
or my new navigator?

21:06.709 --> 21:08.959
