21:18.750 --> 21:21.792
I'm... I'm sorry about your plane.

21:21.875 --> 21:25.333
Listen, nobody's ever stood up
for me before, and...

21:26.041 --> 21:29.583
Well, I have a treasure.
I'll share it with you.

21:29.667 --> 21:31.792
