21:31.875 --> 21:35.166
but I don't think
your bottle cap collection can help.

21:35.250 --> 21:39.542
-No, it's a big glowing jewel!
-Sure, kid.

21:39.625 --> 21:42.542
Why do you think the pirates are after me?

21:42.625 --> 21:45.166
A jewel? You mean it?

21:45.250 --> 21:47.000
I hid it at Louie's.

21:47.750 --> 21:49.959
I could buy back the <i>Sea Duck!</i>

21:50.083 --> 21:53.291
[laughs]
We could buy a whole bunch of <i>Sea Ducks.</i>

21:53.375 --> 21:57.750
Well, how about we go get it first thing
in the morning, you and me.

21:57.834 --> 21:59.959
I'm gone, and we gotta fly.

